  <data name="AboutDescriptionFull" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>DriveFlip is built for the &#x201C;good enough&#x201D; reality of hardware recycling: since NAS data is already fragmented across multiple disks, wiping even one drive with our random-pattern pass makes reconstruction mathematically exhausting. We don&#x2019;t promise a forensic-proof fortress; we provide a sensible, high-speed hurdle that turns &#x201C;recovering your data&#x201D; into an expensive, impractical fool&#x2019;s errand for the next owner.</value>
